  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::EvidenceInteractable
  evidenceId: A3
  evidenceDisplayName: Internal Wi-Fi Reconnection Log
  evidenceDescription: "A network access log showing Alex's registered laptop reconnecting
    to the office Wi-Fi at 10:23 PM \u2014 inside the medical examiner's time-of-death
    window (10:00 PM\u201311:00 PM). Directly contradicts the taxi receipt (A2).
    This is the key piece of physical evidence: Alex was back in the building during
    the murder."
