  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::EvidenceInteractable
  evidenceId: J3
  evidenceDisplayName: "Designer\u2013JP Chat Log"
  evidenceDescription: "An internal messaging log between the Junior Programmer and
    a senior designer. Shows that each of the JP's code submissions that night was
    made in direct response to real-time requirement changes sent by the designer.
    The response times are minutes apart \u2014 it is physically impossible for the
    JP to have committed the murder and returned to active coding within these intervals.
    Eliminates JP."
